
Overview of verb broaden

The verb broaden has 4 senses (first 4 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (9) broaden -- (make broader; "broaden the road")
2. (1) widen, broaden, extend -- (extend in scope or range or area; "The law was extended to all citizens"; "widen the range of applications"; "broaden your horizon"; "Extend your backyard")
3. (1) diversify, branch out, broaden -- (vary in order to spread risk or to expand; "The company diversified")
4. (1) broaden -- (become broader; "The road broadened")
